{"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"PushwooshFramework"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWMessagingDelegate(im)pushwoosh:onMessageOpened:","symbolKind":"method","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"pushwoosh","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)Pushwoosh","text":"Pushwoosh","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"text":"onMessageOpened","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)PWMessage","text":"PWMessage"},{"kind":"text","text":")"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"pushwoosh:onMessageOpened:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"pushwoosh(_:onMessageOpened:)","role":"symbol","required":true},"seeAlsoSections":[{"title":"Related Documentation","identifiers":["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS\/documentation\/PushwooshFramework\/PWMessagingDelegate\/pushwoosh(_:onMessageReceived:)","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS\/documentation\/PushwooshFramework\/Pushwoosh\/delegate"]},{"generated":true,"title":"Handling Notifications","identifiers":["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS\/documentation\/PushwooshFramework\/PWMessagingDelegate\/pushwoosh(_:onMessageReceived:)"]}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS\/documentation\/PushwooshFramework\/PWMessagingDelegate\/pushwoosh(_:onMessageOpened:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS\/documentation\/PushwooshFramework","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS\/documentation\/PushwooshFramework\/PWMessagingDelegate"]]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshframework\/pwmessagingdelegate\/pushwoosh(_:onmessageopened:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]},{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshframework\/pwmessagingdelegate\/pushwoosh(_:onmessageopened:)"]}],"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Called when the user taps on a push notification."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"optional","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"pushwoosh"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"_","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"pushwoosh","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS\/documentation\/PushwooshFramework\/Pushwoosh","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)Pushwoosh","text":"Pushwoosh"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"onMessageOpened"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"message"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"PWMessage","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)PWMessage"},{"kind":"text","text":")"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Overview","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This method is invoked when a user explicitly taps on a notification banner or notification in the Notification Center. Use this method to:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Navigate to relevant content","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Open deep links"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Track user engagement with notifications"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Perform actions based on notification type"}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Timing","level":2,"anchor":"Timing"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"This method is called:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When user taps notification while app is in background"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When user taps notification while app is terminated (app is launched first)"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"NOT called for silent\/background notifications"}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Example","anchor":"Example"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Handle deep links from notification:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["func pushwoosh(_ pushwoosh: Pushwoosh, onMessageOpened message: PWMessage) {","    Analytics.log(\"push_opened\", [","        \"campaign_id\": message.customData?[\"campaign_id\"] ?? \"\"","    ])","","    guard let customData = message.customData else { return }","","    if let deepLink = customData[\"deep_link\"] as? String,","       let url = URL(string: deepLink) {","        DeepLinkRouter.shared.handle(url)","        return","    }","","    if let screen = customData[\"screen\"] as? String {","        navigateToScreen(screen, params: customData)","    }","}","","private func navigateToScreen(_ screen: String, params: [AnyHashable: Any]) {","    switch screen {","    case \"order_details\":","        if let orderId = params[\"order_id\"] as? String {","            router.push(OrderDetailsViewController(orderId: orderId))","        }","    case \"product\":","        if let productId = params[\"product_id\"] as? String {","            router.push(ProductViewController(productId: productId))","        }","    case \"promo\":","        if let promoCode = params[\"promo_code\"] as? String {","            router.push(PromoViewController(code: promoCode))","        }","    default:","        break","    }","}"]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Open specific tab when notification is tapped:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["func pushwoosh(_ pushwoosh: Pushwoosh, onMessageOpened message: PWMessage) {","    guard let tabIndex = message.customData?[\"tab\"] as? Int else { return }","","    if let tabBarController = window?.rootViewController as? UITabBarController {","        tabBarController.selectedIndex = tabIndex","    }","}"]}]}],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS/documentation/PushwooshFramework":{"title":"PushwooshFramework","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshframework","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS\/documentation\/PushwooshFramework","abstract":[{"text":"Push notification SDK for iOS applications.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","role":"collection"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS/documentation/PushwooshFramework/PWMessagingDelegate":{"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"PWMessagingDelegate","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Delegate protocol for handling push notification events."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS\/documentation\/PushwooshFramework\/PWMessagingDelegate","title":"PWMessagingDelegate","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshframework\/pwmessagingdelegate","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"protocol"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"PWMessagingDelegate"}]},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS/documentation/PushwooshFramework/Pushwoosh":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"Pushwoosh"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS\/documentation\/PushwooshFramework\/Pushwoosh","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Main SDK interface for push notification management."}],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshframework\/pushwoosh","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Pushwoosh","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"Pushwoosh"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS/documentation/PushwooshFramework/Pushwoosh/delegate":{"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshfr